>		to read all available information about the people.
>
>		You can do it already, but you have to reopen Fiasco
>		mannually a second time, and open the database. Why not
>		let make this from ARexx?
>	done in Version 1.10.

>AmigaGuide-Documentation:
>		Write this file in a AmigaGuide-file. I think this would be
>		better for reading. I don't create any AmigaGuide-files
>		since now. So I think that this need a little bit time for me.
